# === ANTI_AMNESIA_BEGIN ===
# Claude Code 团队共享配置 vs 个人配置隔离规则
# 设计原理：先整体忽略 .claude/，再用反向规则放行需共享部分
.claude
!.claude/
.claude/*
!.claude/scripts/
!.claude/settings.json
!.claude/scheduled_tasks.json
# 个人笔记与偏好、权限白名单不入库
.claude/notes/
.claude/settings.local.json
# === ANTI_AMNESIA_END ===
